𝐋𝐚𝐮𝐧𝐜𝐡 𝐨𝐟 𝐏𝐞𝐩𝐩𝐞𝐫 𝐒𝐤𝐞𝐭𝐜𝐡𝐛𝐨𝐨𝐤𝐬 
(𝑽𝒐𝒍 𝑶𝒏𝒆 𝒕𝒐 𝑭𝒐𝒖𝒓)

Hi Guys, the Pepper sketchbooks are ready. Enjoy the Launch video as we bring you out to a beautiful indoor garden. 

Let me know if you would like a part 2 where I’ll will answer more of your submitted questions (on @marvelisticstudio stories) and sketch something you have suggested! 

Whenever you have an idea, sketch it down before they are gone. Bring along a sketchbook... or write down your ideas. 
You will be able to develop the ideas in time to come. 

Link in our bio and check out "Pepper Sketchbook"

Notebooks are essentials. We hope each of you can use a notebook that you are proud of, turning an ordinary task of writing or sketching into a great experience. So I’ve partner with @marvelisticstudio to bring you a series of Pepper notebooks!

* 𝙃𝙤𝙬 𝙩𝙤 𝙗𝙪𝙮?

Hi Guys, the Pepper sketchbooks are ready. Enjoy the Launch video as we bring you out to a beautiful indoor garden. 

Let me know if you would like a part 2 where I’ll will answer more of your submitted questions (on @marvelisticstudio stories) and sketch something you have suggested! 

Whenever you have an idea, sketch it down before they are gone. Bring along a sketchbook... or write down your ideas. 
You will be able to develop the ideas in time to come. 

Link in our bio and check out "Pepper Sketchbook"
